id: TYP-mission-command
kind: type
name: Mission command
status: draft
description: One VLM decision: a command kind, its parameters, the reasoning trace, and optional scratchpad fields (progress, next_intent) the model uses to maintain continuity across decisions.
type_kind: record
field: command: TYP-command-kind
field: reasoning: str
field: params: str
field: progress: str
field: next_intent: str
